WEBVTT

00:00:06.187 --> 00:00:09.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
OK, kids,
it’s time to practice our Bible books!

00:00:09.604 --> 00:00:12.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Are you ready
to try the rest of the Hebrew Scriptures?

00:00:12.104 --> 00:00:13.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ready!

00:00:13.687 --> 00:00:18.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jeremiah!
In spite of opposition, he still preached.

00:00:18.645 --> 00:00:23.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Lamentations!
The sadness that God’s people suffered then.

00:00:23.437 --> 00:00:28.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ezekiel!
A watchman who gave warnings faithfully.

00:00:28.229 --> 00:00:33.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Daniel!
Jehovah saved him from the lions’ den.

00:00:33.145 --> 00:00:38.104 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Hosea!
How loyal love surpasses sacrifice.

00:00:38.104 --> 00:00:43.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Joel!
Salvation when God’s Judgment Day begins.

00:00:43.062 --> 00:00:48.020 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Amos!
We need to hate the bad and love the good.

00:00:48.020 --> 00:00:52.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Obadiah!
The Edomites would perish for their sins.

00:00:52.770 --> 00:00:57.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jonah!
God used a fish to turn this man around.

00:00:57.812 --> 00:01:02.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Micah!
Jehovah simply asks that we do good.

00:01:02.854 --> 00:01:07.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Nahum!
God’s prophecy that Nineveh must fall.

00:01:07.437 --> 00:01:12.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Habakkuk!
Jehovah’s day will come right when it should.

00:01:12.604 --> 00:01:17.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Zephaniah!
“The great day of Jehovah [God] is near!”

00:01:17.562 --> 00:01:22.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Haggai!
The precious ones to God are gathered in.

00:01:22.229 --> 00:01:27.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Zechariah!
Has prophecies fulfilled in Jesus Christ.

00:01:27.270 --> 00:01:31.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Malachi!
He told how Jesus’ preaching would begin.

00:01:31.729 --> 00:01:36.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bible
is the greatest book of all.

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:41.729 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah
is its Author, you’ll recall.

00:01:41.729 --> 00:01:46.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s read it ev’ry day
to learn it and obey.

00:01:46.229 --> 00:01:50.479 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The Bible
is the greatest book of all.

